Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE LAST CHALLENGE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:02:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Meruru! Please! Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't die! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't die for someone like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp's a Mage,\Nand yet he's using healing energy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a Sage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that brat have\Nthat much Magic Power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't interfere any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She's alive! Her heart is beating!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The poison's gone! She just might live!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to Popp's\Nimmense healing energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stronger than my Zaoraru spell.\NIt could be Zaoriku-level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Amy, don't let her die! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for Meruru! Come on everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A green light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This light of Courage is Meruru's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She was far braver than I ever was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting her down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,At last.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They did it! Five pillars of light!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it shall shine!\NThe ultimate Purification Spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Minakator!{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Rura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They've all gone to face the Dark King.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They finally did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, mighty Heroes! Defeat the Dark King!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Justice prevails!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, form up around\Nthe Circle of Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy monsters will be weaker\Naround there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll regroup and defend this position!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked. Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where we once fought\Nand lost to Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the tip of Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was pretty torn up,\Nbut it's been fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to make any lame excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make up for\Nthe trouble I caused by fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, try to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp's been in love with you\Nsince he met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's worked really hard\Nto come all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Part of that was probably for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is all too sudden\Nto take in right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Leona, maybe we should all\Nstick close together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the enemy stronghold so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Why can't you put\Nthat aside for now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just I can't handle\Nthis sort of mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But we certainly don't have time to waste.\NLet's hurry, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Minakator...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,An ancient gift from the God of Humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They managed to dig up\Nquite an interesting little trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a slight effect,\Nbut it's not suppressing my Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I can't move Ban Palace now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And its field is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The transfer of my Magic Power\Ninto Ban Palace is likely being blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be more annoying guests now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose this calls for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. We have other guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... This Aura. I remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's your move...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra! What did you do with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but they'll have to face\Nthe Royal Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have but one wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A one-on-one duel against you!\NThat's all I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A duel with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:52.57,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4}MINAKATOR{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:57.57,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}ULTRA COMBUSTION SLASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this somewhere else in Ban Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the tail section of Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My Rura spell brought you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the knight, Sigma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm honored you remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want any interference\Nwhile Lord Hadorra settles things with Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall be dealing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Maam and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Like yourself,\Nthey're somewhere in the citadel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the rear right wing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exciting, Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:10:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We both managed to survive\Nand now we fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing your metal face\Ndoesn't make me feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What a boring response.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just fight already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well then!\NLet me grant your wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The queen, Albinass...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The strongest of the Royal Guard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How unfortunate for you.\NTo have to face me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan just ended up this way.\NDon't hold it against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is your plan to assure victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Sigma take Popp\Nand Hym take Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With a mirror that can reflect spells,\NSigma took Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And Hym has the most experience\Nfighting Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That leaves you against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your analysis of our strategy is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Although you made one slight error.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Aside from Dai, our only real threats\Nare Popp and Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My job is to take on everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to kidnap\Nthat other girl who was with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but that strange creature interfered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we shall lay everything on the line\Nfor a final man-to-man showdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They missed one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:13:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When the light hit us,\NGomechan popped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan protected me\Nfrom the enemy's spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the Rura spell\Nbrought all of us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, Dai, you can't accept\Nsuch a stupid duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra, that goes for you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You turned against Ban, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting Dai here will only serve Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to settle things,\Nthen just wait for another time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer... have any time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he's not backing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you talking about, Dai?!\NYou don't have to go along with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Together we should...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But things are going to get hotter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So I need you to back away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra is already beyond saving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Superior Beings have instant regeneration,\Nbut he's still wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra has little time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:15:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet he's choosing to risk what remains\Nof his life to fight for his honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's chosen me as his opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we have to defeat Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not fight either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,if I don't accept his challenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I won't be able to\Ncall myself a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can yell at me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Honestly...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}how did he grow up this fast?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra, I'll take you on\Nwith every ounce of my might!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this, Dark King Ban!\NThis will be Hadorra's last battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But know that none shall be\Nallowed to interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing so will cost you your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,May you have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra, aren't you being weakened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the Minakator spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel some effect,\Nbut for someone as strong as me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, I'm perfectly fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I guess that means\NDark King Ban is as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing being stalled\Nby the spell is Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban's Magic Power remains unaffected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm actually relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hate for you to be handicapped\Nby the Minakator spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How very touching, you little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We should probably get farther away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The duel between Lord Hadorra\Nand the Hero Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:18:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadorra is beyond the help\Nof any healing spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,His monster body will only decay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To use the last of his life\Nin a fight against the Hero Dai,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a fair fight against his chosen rival,\Nis Lord Hadorra's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My body won't hold up any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have chosen the Hero\Nas my final opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no desire\Nto fight for the Dark King.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I cannot side with\NDai's party, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who took\Nwhat was most precious from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That leaves me but one path left!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To fight the one\Nwho drives me the most
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:19:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and leave my final mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And that opponent is not the Dark King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you hesitating for Albinass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't go through with this
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be nothing but losers, and\NBlock and Fenbren will have died in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't defeat our rivals and show\Nthe honor of the Hadorra Royal Guard
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,how will we face them in the afterlife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go out in a blaze of glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll defeat the Heroes\Nand then fight the Dark King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll show all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you resemble me the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then you're sacrificing yourselves\Nin order to grant Hadorra his last wish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym and Sigma and you as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Albinass, let's stop this.\NWe shouldn't be fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NHow you all feel for Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that's no different from\Nhow we feel about our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We may be enemies, but I can't fight\Nsomeone who feels that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A fight between us is pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Albinass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you all truly care for one another,\Nthen now is when we should stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll help you as much as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, I'm so glad you feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Albinass...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.15,0:21:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're the kind of\Nnaive simpleton that I despise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can kill you without mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.99,0:21:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Needle Thousand!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:12.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:18.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:23.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:29.91,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:35.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:41.88,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:47.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:53.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:59.31,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:01.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:05.23,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:10.36,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:16.79,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:22.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:25.42,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:30.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maam couldn't reach Albinass,\Nwho only acts with Hadorra in mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having decided to sacrifice everything\Nfor him, Albinass attacks unrelentingly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Albinass's intense will\Nslowly backs Maam into a corner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can Maam get through to Albinass?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The warrior of Love will be tested!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.45,0:23:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:23:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Clash of Love"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.00,0:23:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
